Axxess has cut the prices of several uncapped ADSL combo packages. The company said the new prices areÂ in effect and available to new clients. Existing clients on the discounted packages will be charged the new rate from their next billing cycle, while other Axxess clients are able to migrate to the new packages via their Client Control Panel. The packages discounted include 8Mbps, 10Mbps, and 20Mbps uncapped options. The new pricing is shown below.